ğŸ› ï¸ Methods Used

Min-Max Scaling

Scales features between 0 and 1

Useful when features have different ranges

Standard Scaling

Centers data around mean = 0

Scales data to unit variance

Suitable for algorithms like Linear Regression, SVM, and KNN

ğŸ“Š Visualization

